    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Manually operated, electrically powered, public passenger rail vehicles running regularly on exclusive right of way along streets. For more general reference to any low-speed vehicles that run on tracks or by overhead cable, use "trams."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
